---

This product bundles or uses third-party components under their own licenses.
See the "Acknowledgements" section of README.md and the notices below.

• ECDICT — English-Chinese dictionary data (https://github.com/skywind3000/ECDICT)
  Licensed under the MIT License. A subset (~15k exam-tagged words) is bundled.

• Maple Mono — font used for the headword and phonetics
  (https://github.com/subframe7536/maple-font)
  Licensed under the SIL Open Font License 1.1. See
  Sources/FastWords/Fonts/MapleMono-LICENSE.txt for the full text.

• Free Dictionary API (https://dictionaryapi.dev) — optional online lookups
  for example sentences and human pronunciation audio. Used at runtime; no
  code is bundled.
